articles.author: Ben Noll
articles.title: Tropical Cyclone Alfred to lash Queensland and New South Wales, Australia - The Washington Post
articles.description: Significant damage and power outages are possible in the densely populated region of Queensland, where tropical cyclones impacts are not uncommon but direct landfalls are.
articles.content: Tropical Cyclone Alfred, which spawned last week amid a rare trio of tropical cyclones in the South Pacific, is forecast to make landfall in southern Queensland near Brisbane, Australia, on Thursday.… [+3202 chars]
